ea for my son to relax and feel safe. We also played games with him so he could take his mind away from the noisy surroundings.</h3></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-883e" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-lkgTHX jrzygT pf-71_"><div style="--cw:1000px" class="sc-fmBCVi iwpzju"><div class="sc-kfPuZi ihOOoE pf-72_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXEqDS hwCMhq pf-73_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/unnamed_9.jpg?v=1697102132" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/unnamed_9.jpg?v=1697102132 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/unnamed_9_500x.jpg?v=1697102132 320w" width="384" height="512" alt="Celebrating our little wins in Southampton-Portsmouth - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Celebrating our little wins in Southampton-Portsmouth - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-ilfuhL fjsXRa pf-74_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-e2ba" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-lkgTHX jrzygT pf-75_"><div style="--cw:800px" class="sc-fmBCVi iwpzju"><div class="sc-kfPuZi ihOOoE pf-76_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXEqDS hwCMhq pf-77_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brSvTw kXcmVH pf-78_">Celebrating our little wins</h3><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brSvTw kXcmVH pf-80_">Family travel is now an enjoyable experience. Whether it's a road trip or a long-haul flight, my son looks forward to every journey. We still have to explain to him about the upcoming trip so he knows what to expect. He still doesn’t sleep on the plane but is happy to play games and watch movies.<br><br>A few years ago, I had issues with my 